 *
 *   request()  draft   — Business Buyer submits desired products/quantities,
 *                         no prices yet (quote_items.unit_price defaults to
 *                         0.00 until priced).
 *   price()    draft -> sent — Vendor/Inventory Manager sets a unit_price
